title: OUC Update!
body:
http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/sites/default/files/styles/scale_xlarge/public/upload/002971_lol_luna_park_card3_1280x720px_02.jpg?itok=KJutZcky

Hey everyone,

First weekend of the OUC is over and you can stay up to date with the results for each region below. The next round of matches will be played on the **15th of August**!

[**New Zealand**](http://remyrhegaming.com/events/ouc-nz-qualifier/) - Top 4 teams are;

* AuT - Masters of Fate _vs_ UoA - Woofer Doge
* UoA - Dream _vs_ VIC - HKAYCEE

[**Victoria**](http://remyrhegaming.com/events/ouc-vic-qualifier/) - Top 4 teams are;

* Monash A _vs_ RMIT Razors
* MU - Velvet Weifish _vs_ MON - Placeholder

[**South Australia**](http://remyrhegaming.com/events/ouc-sa-qualifier/) - Top 2 teams are;

* University of Adelaide - Khoi Dau Moi _vs_ Succubus Tea Party

[**Queensland**](http://battlefy.com/oce-weekly/oceanic-university-championship-qld-qualifiers/55b9d68bd0b0ff48004ef202/stage/55b9d68bd0b0ff48004ef204/bracket/match/55bc76c6e61f914500f570c1) - top 4 teams are;

* QUT - Team Zabuza _vs_ GU - Everyone but Oscar
* UQ - UQLoL Challenjour Academy _vs_ QUT - QUT3.14s

[**Western Australia**](http://battlefy.com/oce-weekly/oceanic-university-championship-wa-qualifiers/55b9daaae847e84200cfd6f2/stage/55b9daaae847e84200cfd6f4/bracket/match/55bc9c64e61f914500f5711d) - top 4 teams are;

* UWA - UWA _vs_ UWA - Boyz Love
* CU - Curtin League Society _vs_ UWA - Team UWA

[**New South Wales**](http://battlefy.com/oce-weekly/oceanic-university-championship-nsw-qualifiers/55a53b5249ae324800194ee0/stage/55b9d182e847e84200cfd541/bracket/match/55bc6e1c32b21e4100447bd6) - top 4 teams;

* UNSW - Definitely not UNSW _vs_ MU Scorn of the M00n M00n
* UWA - Fear the UWS _vs_ UNSW - Team Phonezone

[**Australia Capital Territory**](http://battlefy.com/oce-weekly/oceanic-university-championship-act-qualifiers/55b9dc62e847e84200cfd76e/stage/55b9dc62e847e84200cfd770/bracket/) - top 4 teams;

* ANU - Sidestep Gaming _vs_ ANU - Team ANU
* UC - Forfeit _vs_ ANU Super Five

Tasmania and Northern territory have 1 team each so they move straight through to the 22nd August top 9 stage.
